{
  "page": "House Grandison",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Grandison of Grandview</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Grandison.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Grandison.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Grandison.svg/250px-House_Grandison.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Grandison.svg/375px-House_Grandison.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Grandison.svg/500px-House_Grandison.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"width:100%;min-width:300px;position:relative;z-index:100;border:0 grey solid;margin-top:-3em;margin-bottom:1em;\"><div style=\"display: table; width: calc(100% - 80px); height: 28px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px; margin: 0px auto 0px; padding: 0;border:0; position: relative; border-collapse:collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &#39;Uncial Antiqua&#39;; color: #000; background: #dd0;\">\n  <div style=\"display:table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding: 4px; clip-path: polygon(2px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 2px calc(100% - 2px)); background: #ff0;\">Rouse Me Not</div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 5px calc(100% - 2px), calc(25% + 3px) 50%, 5px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, 75% 50%, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 2px) 5px, calc(75% + 3px) 50%); background: #ff0;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%, 25% 50%); background: #dd0;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(2px calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 5px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(75% - 3px) 50%, calc(100% - 5px) 2px, 2px 2px, 25% 50%, 2px calc(100% - 2px), 2px 5px, calc(25% - 3px) 50%); background: #ff0;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 75% 50%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); background: #dd0;\"></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA black sleeping lion on yellow<br />(<i>Or, a lion dormant sable</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Grandview\" title=\"Grandview\">Grandview</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Grandison\" title=\"Hugh Grandison\">Hugh Grandison</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Grandview\" title=\"Lord of Grandview\">Lord of Grandview</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Grandison of Grandview</b> is a noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Grandview\" title=\"Grandview\">Grandview</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. They blazon their arms with a black sleeping <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lion</a> on yellow.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> According to semi-canon sources, their words are \"Rouse Me Not\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Grandison_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Grandison at the end of the third century</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Household\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Household</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Historical_Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Grandison\" title=\"Lorent Grandison\">Lorent Grandison</a> served in the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency of Aegon III</a>; <a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a> observed that he loved to sleep.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Grandison\" title=\"Harlan Grandison\">Harlan Grandison</a> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. After dying in his sleep, Harlan was replaced in the White Swords by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Along with <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Cafferen\" title=\"Lord Cafferen\">Lord Cafferen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Grandison\" title=\"Lord Grandison\">Lord Grandison</a> was captured by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battles_at_Summerhall\" title=\"Battles at Summerhall\">battles at Summerhall</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>. Robert then managed to turn the two <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryen</a> loyalists into allies. Lord Grandison was wounded at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a> fighting for Robert, and died of his wounds a year later.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The elderly Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Grandison\" title=\"Hugh Grandison\">Hugh Grandison</a> was among the possible matches offered to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>. When he traveled to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, however, he fell asleep between courses at the welcoming feast.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The aged Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Grandison\" title=\"Hugh Grandison\">Hugh Grandison</a> is sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Narbert_Grandison\" title=\"Narbert Grandison\">Narbert Grandison</a> serves <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>, and he is one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen%27s_men\" title=\"Queen&#39;s men\">queen's men</a> who protect <a href=\"/index.php/Selyse_Florent\" title=\"Selyse Florent\">Selyse Florent</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Narbert yawns during the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Sigorn_and_Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Wedding of Sigorn and Alys Karstark\">wedding of Sigorn and Alys Karstark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Grandison_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Grandison at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Grandison at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Grandisons during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Grandison\" title=\"Hugh Grandison\">Hugh Grandison</a>, Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Grandview\" title=\"Grandview\">Grandview</a>. Called Greybeard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p>With unknown relation to the Lord of the house, there is also:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Narbert_Grandison\" title=\"Narbert Grandison\">Narbert Grandison</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser {<a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Grandison\" title=\"Harlan Grandison\">Harlan Grandison</a>}, a member of <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p>During the time of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>{<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Grandison\" title=\"Lord Grandison\">Lord Grandison</a>} who fought for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battles_at_Summerhall\" title=\"Battles at Summerhall\">battles at Summerhall</a>. Became a loyal ally and friend to <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> after the defeat, but later perished of wounds sustained at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Household\">Household</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Household\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Wagstaff\" title=\"Humfrey Wagstaff\">Humfrey Wagstaff</a> was once the <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> for House Grandison.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Grandison\" title=\"Lorent Grandison\">Lorent Grandison</a>, who became one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regents</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Grandison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.